<!DOCTYPE task PUBLIC "-//OASIS//DTD DITA Task//EN" "task.dtd" []>
<task xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" id="changing-the-target-of-external-xref-to-another-external-target-in-an-existing-document" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="urn:oasis:names:tc:dita:xsd:task.xsd:1.1">
  <title>Changing the Target of External Xref to Another External Target in an Existing Document</title>
  <taskbody>
    <context>
      <p id="change-target-of-external-xref-intro">You can change the target of an external xref to another external target choosing the new target from existing documents.</p>
      <p>Do the following:</p>
    </context>
    <steps>
      <step conref="changing-the-target-of-local-xref.xml#changing-the-target-of-local-xref/step-place-cursor-in-xref">
        <cmd/>
      </step>
      <step id="step-call-change-external-xref-dialog">
        <cmd>Call up the <uicontrol>Change External Xref Dialog</uicontrol>.</cmd>
        <info>
          <p>To call up the <keyword>Change External Xref Dialog</keyword>, choose <menucascade>
              <uicontrol>DITA</uicontrol>
              <uicontrol>Insert External Xref</uicontrol>
            </menucascade> or click the <uicontrol>Insert External Xref</uicontrol> button <image href="insert-external-xreference-button.png" align="center"/> on the toolbar.</p>
        </info>
        <stepresult>
          <p>The <keyword>Change External Xref Dialog</keyword> will appear.</p>
          <fig>
            <title>Change External Xref Dialog.</title>
            <image href="change-external-xref-dialog.png" align="center" placement="break"/>
          </fig>
        </stepresult>
      </step>
      <step conref="changing-the-target-of-xref-from-local-to-external-in-an-existing-document.xml#changing-the-target-of-xref-from-local-to-external-in-an-existing-document/specify-file">
        <cmd/>
      </step>
      <step conref="changing-the-target-of-xref-from-local-to-external-in-an-existing-document.xml#changing-the-target-of-xref-from-local-to-external-in-an-existing-document/specify-target">
        <cmd/>
      </step>
      <step conref="inserting-external-xref-to-existing-document.xml#inserting-external-xref-to-existing-document/specify-attributes-xref">
        <cmd/>
      </step>
      <step conref="changing-the-target-of-local-xref.xml#changing-the-target-of-local-xref/step-change-xref">
        <cmd/>
      </step>
      <step conref="changing-the-target-of-local-xref.xml#changing-the-target-of-local-xref/step-close-dialog-on-change">
        <cmd/>
      </step>
    </steps>
  </taskbody>
</task>
